CHNH SCH QUYN RING T
I. Nguyn tc chung
1. Chnh sch quyn ring t ny (Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T) m t cch thc Cng
ty C phn Vin thng FPT (FPT hoc chng ti) thu thp, tip nhn, tng hp, lu gi, s
dng, x l, tit l, chia s v bo m an ton Thng Tin Khch Hng ca t chc, c nhn
(Khch Hng hoc qu khch), bao gm khch hng, i l, nh cung cp, nh thu v i
tc: (i) s dng cc dch v c cung cp bi FPT; (ii) truy cp, s dng cc knh tng tc
khch hng thuc s hu ca FPT, bao gm nhng khng gii hn: website www.fpt.com.vn,
ng dng HealthCare, cc website v hi nhm trn cc trang mng x hi (nh Facebook,...)
thuc s hu ca FPT (Knh FPT) (cc mc (i) v (ii) sau y c gi chung l Dch V).
2. Thng Tin Khch Hng l bt k thng tin, d liu no c th c s dng nhn
dng Khch Hng hoc da vo m Khch Hng c xc nh, chng hn nh tn, quc
tch, s in thoi, chi tit th thanh ton v ngn hng, s thch c nhn, a ch email, a
im, hnh nh, thng tin CMND/th cn cc cng dn, ngy sinh, tnh trng hn nhn, thng
tin bo him, thng tin giao dch, lch s truy cp, hnh trnh khch hng, d liu sinh trc
hc, h s bnh n/sc khe.
3. Khch Hng c, hiu, ng vi ni dung ca Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T. Ti
tng thi im, FPT c th sa i, b sung, v/hoc cp nht Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T
ny. FPT s ng ti Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T c sa i, b sung v/hoc cp nht trn
website www.fpt.com.vn. Vic Khch Hng tip tc s dng, truy cp Knh FPT, tip tc s
dng cc Dch V c hiu l Khch Hng ng vi ni dung Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T
sa i, b sung, v/hoc cp nht .
4. Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T c lp bng ting Vit.
5. Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T ny bao gm cc ni dung sau:
5.1 Thng Tin Khch Hng c chng ti thu thp
5.2 Cch thc chng ti bo v Thng Tin Khch Hng
5.3 Cch thc chng ti s dng Thng Tin Khch Hng
5.4 Cch thc chng ti chia s Thng Tin Khch Hng
5.5 Truy cp v la chn
5.6 Thng tin lin lc, thng bo v sa i
5.7 Mt s thng tin b sung cho chu u
5.8 Ph lc 1: Thng tin khch hng c thu thp trong qu trnh s dng ng
dng HealthCare
II. Thng Tin Khch Hng c chng ti thu thp
Chng ti thu thp Thng Tin Khch Hng trong qu trnh cung cp Dch V cho qu
khch. Di y l cc loi thng tin c chng ti thu thp:
1. Thng tin qu khch cung cp cho chng ti
a) Chng ti thu thp bt k thng tin no qu khch cung cp lin quan n Dch V
trong qu
trnh tin hnh nhng hot ng nh (i) s dng Dch V hoc tham gia cc d n/ ti
nghin cu khoa hc, th nghim lm sng do FPT thc hin; (ii) thc hin ng k m ti
khon, ng nhp, tng tc vi cc Knh FPT; (iii) tham gia cc hi tho, s kin khch hng,
cuc thi, tr chi, cuc kho st/iu tra hoc s kin khc do FPT t chc; (iv) s dng chc
nng sinh trc hc nhn din c nhn, xc thc giao dch;...
b) Khch hng c trch nhim m bo nhng thng tin Khch Hng cung cp l y ,
chnh xc v cp nht nht nhm m bo quyn li ca Khch Hng theo quy nh ca vic
s dng dch v tng ng. FPT khng chu trch nhim trong trng hp Khch Hng cung
cp thng tin khng chnh xc hoc khng y theo quy nh ca Dch V.
c) Vi nhng Khch Hng cha 18 tui, vui lng m bo c y s ng v
chp thun ca cha, m hoc ngi i din hp php i vi vic cung cp cc Thng Tin
Khch Hng cho FPT; cha, m hoc ngi i din s chu rng buc bi Chnh Sch Quyn
Ring T ny v chu trch nhim i vi hnh vi ca Khch Hng. FPT c quyn t chi
Khch Hng tip cn Knh FPT hoc cung cp cc Dch V c lin quan trong trng hp c
cn c rng Khch Hng cha 18 tui cha c c s ng v chp thun ni trn t
cha, m hoc ngi i din hp php.
d) Trong trng hp Khch Hng cung cp thng tin ca bt k bn th ba no, Khch
Hng cam oan v bo m rng Khch Hng c c y s ng v chp thun ca
bn th ba i vi vic Khch Hng cung cp thng tin cho FPT v i vi vic FPT s
dng cc thng tin theo cch thc v quy nh ti Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T ny. FPT s
khng chu bt k trch nhim no i vi bn th ba trong trng hp Khch Hng cung
cp thng tin m cha c s ng hoc chp thun ca bn th ba . Trong trng hp
ny, Khch Hng s chu mi trch nhim pht sinh t hnh vi cung cp thng tin gy ra, bao
gm c vic gii quyt, bng chi ph ca Khch Hng, bt k khiu ni/khiu kin no ca bn
th ba i vi Khch Hng v/hoc FPT, bi hon cho FPT bt k khon tin no m FPT phi
tr cho bn th ba, nu c, lin quan n khiu ni/khiu kin nu trn.
2. Thng tin t ng: Chng ti t ng thu thp mt s loi thng tin nht nh khi qu
khch tng tc vi Dch V.
FPT c quyn thu thp cc thng tin, d liu lin quan n hot ng m Khch Hng
thc hin trong khun kh Dch V, bao gm nhng khng gii hn thng tin, d liu v
cc bn cung cp dch v, hng ha cho Khch Hng, thng tin giao dch m Khch Hng thc
hin (loi hng ha, dch v, a im, thi gian giao dch), phng thc thanh ton (khng
lu gi cc d liu quan trng ca th thanh ton c s dng cho vic thanh ton bao gm
s th chi tit, s CVV hoc m s xc thc khc c gi tr php l tng ng), thng tin
thit b (nh a ch IP, h iu hnh, loi trnh duyt, thng s phn cng, UDID, MEIDs, nh
v, a ch ca trang web gii thiu (nu c), cc trang m Khch Hng gh thm t Knh FPT
v cc ng dng di ng, s ln truy cp, phn hi, tn tp, phin bn v nhn dng qung
co v cc thng tin lin quan khc (nu c)).
3. Thu thp v s dng cookies:
a) Chng ti s dng cookie, pixel v cc cng ngh tng t khc (gi chung l cookie)
nhn din trnh duyt hoc thit b ca qu khch, tm hiu thm v s thch ca qu
khch, cung cp cho qu khch cc tnh nng v dch v thit yu v cho cc mc ch b sung
khc, bao gm:
b) Nhn din qu khch khi qu khch ng nhp s dng Dch V ca chng ti. iu
ny cho php chng ti cung cp cho qu khch cc xut, hin th ni dung c c nhn
ha v cung cp cc tnh nng v dch v ty chnh khc.
c) Lu tm n cc ty chn m qu khch chp thun. iu ny cho php chng ti
tn trng nhng iu qu khch thch v khng thch, chng hn nh ngn ng v cu hnh
m qu khch la chn.
d) Tin hnh nghin cu v phn tch ci thin Dch V ca chng ti.
e) Ngn chn hnh vi gian ln.
f) Ci thin an ninh.
g) Cung cp ni dung, bao gm qung co, c lin quan n s thch ca qu khch trn
cc trang web ca chng ti v trang web ca bn th ba.
h) o lng v phn tch cht lng ca cc Dch V.
i) Cookie cho php qu khch tn dng mt s tnh nng cn thit ca chng ti. V d,
nu qu khch chn hoc t chi cookie ca chng ti, qu khch s khng th s dng mt
s sn phm, dch v nht nh yu cu qu khch ng nhp hoc qu khch c th phi t
tay iu chnh mt s ty chn hoc ci t ngn ng mi khi qu khch truy cp li cc trang
web ca chng ti.
j) Cc bn th ba c chp thun cng c th t cookie khi qu khch tng tc vi
cc Dch V. Cc bn th ba ny thng bao gm cc cng c tm kim, nh cung cp dch v
o lng v phn tch, mng x hi v cc cng ty qung co. Cc bn th ba s dng cookie
trong qu trnh cung cp ni dung, bao gm qung co lin quan n s thch ca qu khch,
o lng hiu qu ca qung co v thc hin mt s dch v thay mt cho chng ti.
k) Qu khch c th qun l cookie trnh duyt bng vic ci t trnh duyt ca mnh.
Tnh nng 'Tr gip' trn hu ht cc trnh duyt s cho qu khch bit cch ngn trnh duyt
chp nhn cc cookie mi, cch trnh duyt thng bo cho qu khch khi qu khch nhn
c cookie mi, cch tt cookie v khi cookie ht hn. Nu qu khch tt tt c cookie trn
trnh duyt ca mnh, c chng ti v bn th ba s khng th chuyn cookie sang trnh duyt
ca qu khch. Tuy nhin, nu qu khch lm iu ny, qu khch c th phi t tay iu
chnh mt s ty chn mi khi qu khch truy cp li trang web v mt s tnh nng v dch
v c th khng hot ng.
4. Thng tin t cc ngun khc: Chng ti c th thu thp thng tin v qu khch t cc
ngun khc, bao gm nh cung cp dch v, i tc v cc ngun cng khai c sn.
III. Cch thc chng ti bo v Thng Tin Khch Hng
1. Ti FPT, bo mt l u tin cao nht ca chng ti. H thng ca chng ti c thit
k c tnh n kh nng bo m an ton v ring t cho thng tin ca qu khch. Mi Thng
Tin Khch Hng u c lu gi v bo mt bi h thng ca FPT hoc n v cung cp dch
v cho FPT theo quy nh ca php lut v Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T ny.
2. Khi thu thp d liu, FPT s n lc ti a trong phm vi cho php thc hin vic
lu gi v bo mt Thng Tin Khch Hng ti h thng my ch v cc Thng Tin Khch Hng
ny c bo m an ton bng cc h thng tng la, cc bin php kim sot truy cp,
m ha d liu. FPT c cc bin php thch hp v k thut v an ninh ngn chn ti a
trong phm vi c th vic truy cp, s dng tri php Thng Tin Khch Hng. FPT cng
thng xuyn phi hp vi cc chuyn gia bo mt nhm cp nht nhng thng tin mi nht
v an ninh mng m bo s an ton cho Thng Tin Khch Hng.
3. Cc thng tin th thanh ton ca qu khch do cc t chc ti chnh pht hnh c
chng ti bo v theo tiu chun quc t vi nguyn tc khng lu gi cc d liu quan trng
ca th thanh ton (s th, h tn, s CVV hoc m s xc thc khc c gi tr php l tng
ng) trn h thng ca chng ti. Giao dch thanh ton ca qu khch c thc hin trn
h thng ca ngn hng lin quan hoc n v lin kit/hp tc dch v thng qua Knh FPT.
4. Khch Hng tuyt i khng s dng cc cng c, chng trnh hay bin php no
khc can thip tri php vo h thng hay lm thay i cu trc d liu ca bt k Dch V
no, cng nh thc hin bt k hnh vi no khc nhm pht tn, c v cho cc hot ng vi
mc ch can thip, ph hoi hay xm nhp vo d liu ca h thng FPT, cng nh cc cc
hnh vi phm php lut Vit Nam. Trong trng hp chng ti pht hin qu khch c hnh
vi vi phm, chng ti c quyn chuyn thng tin v hnh vi vi phm cho cc c quan c thm
quyn x l theo quy nh php lut.
5. Qu khch c trch nhim bo v thng tin ti khon ca mnh v khng cung cp bt
k thng tin no lin quan n ti khon, mt khu hay cc phng thc xc thc (vd: OTP)
truy cp trn cc website, ng dng, phn mm v cc cng c khc (nu c).
6. Chng ti lu tr Thng Tin Khch Hng m bo cho qu khch kh nng s dng
lin tc cc Dch V, v lu tr trong thi hn cn thit thc hin c cc Mc ch, hoc
theo quy nh ca php lut (bao gm c cho mc ch thu v k ton), hoc thc hin
cc cng vic khc nh c thng bo trc cho qu khch. Thi gian chng ti lu gi
Thng Tin Khch Hng c th khc nhau ty thuc vo Mc ch. Khi Thng Tin Khch Hng
khng cn cn thit cho vic cung cp Dch V hoc Mc ch hoc FPT khng cn c mc
ch kinh doanh hoc php l gi li Thng Tin Khch Hng, chng ti s thc hin cc
bc ngn chn vic truy cp hoc s dng Thng Tin Khch Hng cho bt k mc ch
no ngoi vic tun th theo Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T ny, hoc cho mc ch an ton, bo
mt, pht hin v phng chng gian ln; hoc xa phn thng tin nh danh thuc Thng Tin
Khch Hng theo quy nh php lut.
7. Thng Tin Khch Hng c th c lu tr ti, truy cp t hoc chuyn n nhiu
quc gia, bao gm c Vit Nam. Khi chng ti chuyn Thng Tin Khch Hng ca qu khch
n cc quc gia khc, chng ti s m bo rng thng tin c chuyn theo Chnh Sch
Quyn Ring T ny v c cho php theo php lut v quy nh lin quan.
IV. Cch thc chng ti s dng Thng Tin Khch Hng
Chng ti s dng Thng Tin Khch Hng vn hnh, cung cp v ci thin Dch V cho cc
mc ch (Mc ch) bao gm:
1. Cung cp Dch V: Chng ti s dng Thng Tin Khch Hng :
a) cung cp Dch V v x l cc giao dch lin quan n Dch V, bao gm ng k v
thanh ton;
b) xut Dch V m qu khch c th quan tm, nhn din s thch ca qu khch v
c nhn ha tri nghim ca qu khch vi Dch V;
c) thc hin cc hot ng ni b cn thit cung cp dch v, bao gm khc phc cc
li phn mm v sur c vn hnh, tin hnh phn tch d liu, th nghim v nghin cu,
gim st v phn tch xu hng s dng v hot ng;
d) bo v tnh bo mt hoc tnh ton vn ca Dch V v mi phng tin hoc thit b
c s dng cung; cp Dch V;
e) xc nhn cc giao dch v thc hin cc khon thanh ton;
f) to mi, qun tr v cp nht ti khon Khch Hng, xc minh danh tnh Khch Hng;
g) cho php tng tc gia Khch Hng vi FPT hay gia Ngi Dng vi cc i tc
c lin kt (nu c);
2. o lng, h tr v ci thin Dch V: Chng ti s dng Thng Tin Khch Hng o
lng vic s dng, phn tch hiu sut, sa li, cung cp h tr, ci thin v pht trin Dch
V.
3. Tun th ngha v php l: Chng ti c ngha v php l thu thp, s dng hoc
lu tr Thng Tin Khch Hng ca qu khch trong mt s trng hp nht nh, bao gm
khi c yu cu, c t vn, ngh hoc i hi bi cc c vn php l hoc bt k quy
nh php lut, vn bn di lut, vn bn hoc yu cu ca chnh ph hay cc c quan c
thm quyn ti a phng hoc nc ngoi, yu cu ca c quan nh nc c thm quyn
bao gm nhng khng gii hn ngha v cng b thng tin, bo co theo quy nh php lut
v khuyn mi, lu tr h s, kim ton, iu tra v gii quyt khiu ni hoc tranh chp,
tun th cc lnh ca ta n hoc cc yu cu php l, vn bn hoc yu cu ca chnh ph
hoc quy nh khc; hoc cc tha thun khc; v bo v quyn hoc ti sn ca chng ti
trong trng hp khiu ni hoc tranh chp.
4. Lin lc vi qu khch: Chng ti s dng Thng Tin Khch Hng lin lc vi qu
khch lin quan n Dch V thng qua cc knh khc nhau (v d: email, chat) v tr li
yu cu ca qu khch.
5. Tip th: Chng ti s dng Thng Tin Khch Hng tip th v qung b Dch V.
Chng ti c th hin th qung co Dch V da trn s thch ca qu khch.
6. Phng chng gian ln v lm dng, ri ro ti sn v tn dng: Chng ti s dng Thng
Tin Khch Hng ngn chn v pht hin gian ln v lm dng nhm bo v an ninh ca
khch hng, chng ti v nhng ngi khc. Chng ti cng c th s dng cc phng php
chm im nh gi v qun tr ri ro ti sn v tn dng.
7. Mt s mc ch c th cn s ng ca qu khch: Chng ti c th xin chp thun
ca qu khch v vic s dng Thng Tin Khch Hng cho mt mc ch c th no khi
chng ti lin h vi qu khch.
V. Cch thc chng ti chia s Thng Tin Khch Hng
Thng tin v khch hng l mt phn quan trng trong hot ng ca chng ti, v chng ti
khng bn Thng Tin Khch Hng ca khch hng cho ngi khc. Chng ti ch chia s
Thng Tin Khch Hng nh c nu di y v trong phm vi php lut cho php. Cc bn
th ba nhn Thng Tin Khch Hng theo ng Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T u tun th Chnh
Sch Quyn Ring T ny, chnh sch tng t khc v cc quy nh php lut c lin quan.
1. Thc hin theo yu cu ca cc c quan nh nc c thm quyn, hoc theo quy nh
ca php lut;
2. Giao dch lin quan n bn th ba: Chng ti cung cp cho qu khch cc dch v,
phn mm v ni dung do bn th ba cung cp s dng trn hoc thng qua Dch V. Qu
khch c th bit khi no bn th ba tham gia vo cc giao dch ca qu khch v chng ti
s chia s thng tin lin quan + n cc giao dch vi bn th ba .
3. Bn th ba cung cp dch v: Chng ti s dng v/hoc hp tc vi cc cng ty v c
nhn khc thc hin mt s cng vic thay mt chng ti. V d bao gm: gi thng tin
lin lc, x l thanh ton, nh gi ri ro tn dng v tun th, phn tch d liu, cung cp h
tr tip th v bn hng (bao gm qun l qung co v s kin), qun l quan h khch hng
v o to. Cc bn th ba cung cp dch v ny c quyn truy cp vo Thng Tin Khch Hng
cn thit thc hin cc chc nng ca h, nhng khng c s dng cho cc mc ch
khc. Ngoi ra, h phi tun th Chnh sch quyn ring t ny v php lut v bo v quyn
ring t lin quan.
4. Ti cu trc, Chuyn nhng doanh nghip: Trong qu trnh pht trin kinh doanh,
chng ti c th bn hoc mua cc doanh nghip hoc ti cu trc doanh nghip hoc dch v
khc ph hp vi quy nh ca php lut. Trong cc giao dch nh vy, Thng Tin Khch
Hng, c s d liu v quyn s dng thng tin ni chung l mt trong nhng ti sn kinh
doanh c chuyn nhng nhng bn nhn chuyn nhng vn phi tun theo cc quy
nh ca Chnh sch quyn ring t ny (hoc khi c khch hng chp thun). Ngoi ra,
trong trng hp FPT hoc phn ln ti sn ca FPT c mt cng ty khc mua, thng tin
ca qu khch s tr thnh mt trong nhng ti sn c chuyn nhng.
5. Bo v chng ti v nhng ngi khc: Chng ti tit l ti khon v Thng Tin Khch
Hng khc khi chng ti tin rng vic l ph hp tun th php lut, thc thi hoc
p dng cc iu khon v tha thun khc ca chng ti hoc bo v quyn, ti sn hoc
an ninh ca chng ti, khch hng ca chng ti, hoc bt k ngi no khc. Cc cng vic
nu trn c th bao gm vic trao i thng tin vi cc cng ty v t chc khc ngn chn
v pht hin gian ln v gim ri ro tn dng.
6. Ty theo s la chn ca qu khch: Ngoi cc trng hp nu trn, qu khch s
nhn c thng bo khi Thng Tin Khch Hng v qu khch c th c chia s vi bn
th ba v la chn ca qu khch i vi vic chia s thng tin.
7. Nhng trng hp chia s khng phi xin chp thun: Theo quy nh ca php lut
hin hnh, cc Thng Tin Khch Hng thuc thng tin y t ca qu khch, theo quyt nh
ca ngi chu trch nhim ca c s khm bnh cha bnh, c th c chng ti chia s
nhm nng cao cht lng chn on, chm sc, iu tr ngi bnh gia nhng ngi hnh
ngh trong nhm trc tip iu tr cho ngi bnh; hoc cho mt s i tng khai thc h
s, bao gm sinh vin thc tp, nghin cu vin, ngi hnh ngh trong c s khm bnh,
cha bnh c mn h s bnh n ti ch c hoc sao chp phc v cho vic nghin
cu hoc cng tc chuyn mn k thut; hoc theo yu cu ca c quan c thm quyn ca
Vit Nam.
VI. Truy cp v la chn
1. Tr trng hp php lut c quy nh khc, qu khch c th xem, cp nht v xa
mt s thng tin nht nh v ti khon v cc tng tc ca qu khch vi Dch V. Nu qu
khch khng th t truy cp hoc cp nht thng tin ca mnh, qu khch lun c th lin h
vi chng ti c h tr.
2. Qu khch c nhiu la chn v vic thu thp v s dng Thng Tin Khch Hng.
Nhiu Dch V bao gm chc nng cho php qu khch ty chn v cch thng tin ca qu
khch ang c s dng. Qu khch c th chn khng cung cp mt s thng tin nht nh,
nhng sau qu khch c th khng tn dng c mt s Dch V.
a) Thng tin ti khon: Nu qu khch mun b sung, cp nht hoc xa thng tin lin
quan n ti khon ca mnh, vui lng gi email n a ch hotrokhachhang@fpt.com.vn v
thc hin theo hng dn ca FPT. Khi qu khch cp nht hoc xa bt k thng tin no,
chng ti thng gi mt bn sao ca phin bn trc v mc ch k thut.
b) Lin lc: Nu qu khch khng mun nhn tin nhn qung co t chng ti, vui lng
hy ng k hoc iu chnh ty chn lin lc ca qu khch, vui lng gi email n a ch
hotrokhachhang@fpt.com.vn v thc hin theo hng dn ca FPT. Nu qu khch khng
mun nhn thng bo trong ng dng t chng ti, vui lng iu chnh ci t thng bo
trong ng dng hoc thit b ca qu khch.
c) Qung co: Nu qu khch khng mun xem qung co da trn s thch, vui lng vui
lng gi email n a ch hotrokhachhang@fpt.com.vn v thc hin theo hng dn ca
FPT.
d) Trnh duyt v thit b: Tnh nng Tr gip trn hu ht cc trnh duyt v thit b s
cho qu khch bit cch ngn trnh duyt hoc thit b ca mnh chp nhn cookie mi, lm
th no trnh duyt thng bo cho qu khch khi qu khch nhn c cookie mi hoc
cch tt hn chc nng cookie.
VII. Thng tin lin lc, thng bo v sa i
1. Hot ng kinh doanh ca chng ti lin tc thay i v Chnh Sch Quyn Ring T
ny cng c th c sa i. Qu khch nn truy cp v kim tra trang web ca chng ti
thng xuyn cp nht nhng thay i gn nht. Tr trng hp c quy nh khc, Chnh
Sch Quyn Ring T hin ti ca chng ti p dng cho tt c Thng Tin Khch Hng chng
ti c v qu khch v ti khon ca qu khch.
Nu qu khch c bt k cu hi no v quyn ring t ti FPT hoc mun lin h vi n v
kim sot thng tin ca chng ti, vui lng lin h vi chng ti v chng ti s c gng tr
li cu hi ca qu khch. Qu khch cng c th lin h vi chng ti theo a ch di y:
hotrokhachhang@fpt.com.vn
VIII. Mt s thng tin b sung cho chu u
Chng ti cung cp thm mt s thng tin v quyn ring t, vic thu thp v s dng Thng
Tin Khch Hng ca khch hng tim nng v khch hng hin ti ca chng ti ti cc quc
gia thuc Lin Minh Chu u.
1. n V Kim Sot Thng Tin Khch Hng. Cng ty C phn Vin thng FPT (Tng 9,
Block A, ta nh FPT Cu Giy, s 10 Phm Vn Bch, qun Cu Giy, TP. H Ni) l n v
kim sot cc Thng Tin Khch Hng c thu thp hoc x l theo Chnh sch quyn ring
t ny.
2. X l. Chng ti x l Thng Tin Khch Hng da trn mt hoc mt s c s php l
sau y:
a) Cn thit k kt hp ng vi qu khch hoc vi t chc m qu khch i din,
thc hin cc ngha v hp ng, cung cp cc Dch V, phn hi cc yu cu t qu
khch, hoc h tr khch hng;
b) Khi chng ti c li ch hp php, nh c m t Mc 2 ca Chnh sch quyn ring
t
c) Cn thit tun th php lut v cc ngha v php l;
d) tr li cc yu cu hp php; hoc
e) Da trn s chp thun ca qu khch.
3. Quyn ca qu khch. Theo quy nh ca php lut, qu khch c cc quyn sau:
a) hi chng ti c ang nm gi Thng Tin Khch Hng v bn thn hay khng v yu
cu cung cp bn sao Thng Tin Khch Hng v thng tin v cch thc cc thng tin
c x l;
b) yu cu nh chnh Thng Tin Khch Hng khng chnh xc;
c) yu cu loi b Thng Tin Khch Hng khng cn cn thit cho cc mc ch x l, cc
thng tin c x l da trn s chp thun nhng chp thun c rt li, hoc thng
tin c x l khng tun th cc quy nh ca php lut hin hnh;
d) yu cu chng ti tm dng x l Thng Tin Khch Hng khi hot ng x l khng
ph hp;
e) phn i vic x l d liu c nhn;
f) yu cu lun chuyn Thng Tin Khch Hng m qu khch cung cp cho chng ti
(khng bao gm thng tin c c t cc thng tin c thu thp), trong trng hp vic x
l Thng Tin Khch Hng c thc hin trn c s s ng hoc hp ng vi qu
khch v c thc hin bng phng thc t ng; v
g) gi khiu ni vi c quan c thm quyn nu qu khch tin rng chng ti vi phm
quyn ring t ca mnh.
Qu khch c th thc hin cc quyn truy cp, nh chnh, xa, yu cu tm dng,
phn i v yu cu lun chuyn thng tin bng cch lin h vi chng ti. Nu qu khch
mun thc hin bt k quyn g nu trn v qu khch l khch hng ca chng ti, vui lng
lin h vi chng ti. Nu qu khch khng phi l khch hng ca chng ti, vui lng lin h
vi chng ti theo a ch ti Mc V trn.
Khi qu khch ng cho chng ti x l Thng Tin Khch Hng ca mnh cho mt
mc ch c th, qu khch c th rt li s ng bt c lc no v chng ti s ngng
mi hot ng x l d liu ca qu khch cho mc ch .
4. Chuyn thng tin ra ngoi Lin Minh Chu. Khi chng ti chuyn Thng Tin Khch
Hng c thu thp v lu tr ti Lin Minh Chu ra ngoi Lin Minh Chu, chng ti s thc
hin theo cc iu khon ca Chnh sch quyn ring t ny v php lut bo v quyn ring
t hin hnh. iu ny c th bao gm vic chuyn d liu theo cc tha thun chuyn d
liu c bao gm iu khon hp ng tiu chun c y ban Chu ph duyt.
PH LC 1 - THNG TIN KHCH HNG C THU THP TRONG QU TRNH S
DNG NG DNG HEALTHCARE
(km theo Chnh sch Quyn ring t ca Cng ty C phn Vin thng FPT)
Trong qu trnh qu khch s dng ng dng HealthCare, chng ti thu thp Thng Tin
Khch Hng c th nh sau:
1. Thng tin qu khch cung cp cho chng ti: khi qu khch thc hin to v qun l
ti khon, chng ti s yu cu qu khch cung cp cc thng tin bao gm: Tn, tui, a ch
email, ngy thng nm sinh, a ch thng tr, a ch lin h, s in thoi v thng tin lin
lc tng t khc; tn ngi dng, gii tnh, lin kt ngi thn, b danh, vai tr v thng tin
xc thc v bo mt khc; Thng tin lin quan n danh tnh, bao gm thng tin nhn dng
do chnh ph cp, quc tch; Thng tin lin quan n tnh trng bnh i tho ng ca qu
khch: Cc thng tin ny s c chng ti s dng xut dch v m qu khch c th
quan tm, nhn din s thch/hin trng sc khe ca qu khch v c nhn ha tri nghim
ca qu khch i vi ng dng HealthCare (ng Dng);
2. Thng tin chng ti nhn c t vic qu khch s dng cc tnh nng thuc ng Dng
bao gm:
a) Thng tin v hnh vi s dng ng Dng: ni dung qu khch xem hoc tm kim,
thi gian phn hi ca ng Dng v cc thng tin tng tc trang (nh cun, nhp) nhm
thc hin cc hot ng ni b cn thit cung cp dch v, bao gm khc phc cc li phn
mm v s c vn hnh, ti u tri nghim trong qu trnh s dng, tin hnh phn tch d
liu, th nghim v nghin cu.
b) Thng tin thit b: Thng tin mng v kt ni (SSID/ BSSID), nh a ch giao thc
Internet (IP) c s dng kt ni thit b di ng vi Internet v thng tin v nh cung
cp dch v Internet hay thng tin trng thi in thoi ca qu khch
(READ_PHONE_STATE) nhn bit trng thi cuc gi trong tnh nng t vn sc khe t
xa, gip bc s nhn bit c kt ni c thc hin t vn hay khng, gip cuc gi t vn
sc khe t xa khng b gin on bi cc cuc gi t cc nn tng khc trn thit b.
c) Thng tin bluetooth: ng Dng yu cu cp quyn truy cp Bluetooth (BLUETOOTH/
BLUETOOTH_ADMIN) trn in thoi qu khch c th kt ni vi: thit b kim tra ng
huyt c nhn ca FPT ng b d liu t thit b ny vi ng dng HealthCare; cc thit
b m thanh (loa/tai nghe khng dy) phc v qu trnh tng tc gia bc s v khch
hng khi s dng tnh nng t vn sc khe t xa.
d) Truy cp CAMERA trn thit b: ng Dng yu cu cp quyn truy cp s dng
CAMERA trn in thoi ca qu khch c v nhn dng m QRCode - m y t nh danh
khch hng ti FPT, v phc v qu trnh tng tc gia bc s v khch hng khi s dng
tnh nng t vn sc khe t xa;
e) Truy cp m thanh trn thit b: ng Dng yu cu cp quyn truy cp s dng m
thanh (RECORD_AUDIO) trn in thoi ca qu khch thc hin cuc gi thoi gia bc
s v khch hng khi s dng tnh nng t vn sc khe t xa.
f) Cc thng tin khc: Truy cp b nh thit b: nh, tp tin, video
(READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE), FPT cung cp dch v h
tr chnh xc nht vi nhu cu ca qu khch, hoc gip bc s a ra t vn chnh xc vi
thng thng sc khe ca qu khch thng qua hnh nh, video. Chng ti s yu cu qu
khch cho php ng dng truy cp vo kho hnh nh, file lu tr vi cc tnh nng cn truy
cp cc d liu ny. Nu khng cho php qu khch s khng th tn dng cc tnh nng ny.
g) Thng tin nhn dng v thng tin cookie: nhn din thit b ca qu khch, tm hiu
thm v s thch ca qu khch, cung cp cho qu khch cc tnh nng v dch v thit yu
v cho cc mc ch b sung khc.
